      ><div>Hi there,&nbsp;</div>
          <div><span style="word-spacing: normal;"><br></span></div>
          <div>
            <div>We're thrilled to announce: <b>
                <font color="#32a956"><a href="https://www.trae.ai/solo" target="_blank" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;" tabindex="-1">TRAE SOLO</a></font> is now officially launched globally
              </b>. With this launch, we've redefined what it means to be responsive. SOLO doesn't just respond to context — it responds to <b>you</b>, your <b>feedback</b>, and your <b>workflow</b>. From <b>November 11, 8:00 PM to November 15, 7:59 AM (PST)</b>, we are offering <b>free access to all users</b> for a limited time. Come and experience <font color="#32a956"><a href="https://www.trae.ai/solo" target="_blank" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;" tabindex="-1">SOLO</a></font> now!</div>
            <div><br></div>
            <div>
              <font size="4" color="#32a956"><b>SOLO: Responsive, Redefined</b></font>
            </div>
            <div>SOLO now adapts across 3 key dimensions that make collaboration with AI truly dynamic:</div>
          </div>
          <div><br></div>
          <div><b>
              <font size="4" color="#32a956">Responsive Review</font>
            </b></div>
          <div>SOLO adapts in real time to your <b>reviews, feedback, and direction</b>. It's a genuine <b>back-and-forth between you and the agent</b>, closing the gap between human intent and AI execution — so developers and agents stay perfectly in sync.</div>
